summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Page 24-341 of the Seattle Municipal Code as amended by Page 320 of Volume III of said Code (Plat 45E, Page 119 of the official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300), to rezone certain property located on both sides of Yesler Way between Empire Way and 29th Avenue from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone. (Petition of Edward Buchanan; C.F. 290729.
